main event: A 15-year-old reported observing two unidentified objects moving southerly in the sky for 2 to 5 minutes in Silver Grove, Kentucky on February 3, 1963.
interesting points: The witness has a history of reporting similar sightings reliably,The objects were observed for a duration of 2 to 5 minutes,Visual and radar confirmation suggests the objects could be real,The nature and purpose of the objects remain unknown,One object was described as about the size of a quarter and dimmed before disappearing.
sighted object: two unidentified objects in the sky
